{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2012-07-blogging-with-blogger/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>So my move to Blogger from a self-hosted wordpress blog is complete. Images you upload in your post directly go to your Picasa account and get served via the Google CDN. I've also integrated the website of my\n<a href=\"http://www.urvikhanna.com/2010/11/inventivbiz-creative-solutions-for.html\">advertising firm</a>\ninto my blog -- since the idea of a company website was to primarily showcase portfolio. Â Less time spent on software management and more time for the fun stuff!</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"blogbg\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3b37ea6ce68daa53e146c79ed0ee1530/6aca1/blogbg.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3b37ea6ce68daa53e146c79ed0ee1530/d2f63/blogbg.jpg 163w,\n/static/3b37ea6ce68daa53e146c79ed0ee1530/c989d/blogbg.jpg 325w,\n/static/3b37ea6ce68daa53e146c79ed0ee1530/6aca1/blogbg.jpg 650w,\n/static/3b37ea6ce68daa53e146c79ed0ee1530/7c09c/blogbg.jpg 975w,\n/static/3b37ea6ce68daa53e146c79ed0ee1530/01ab0/blogbg.jpg 1300w,\n/static/3b37ea6ce68daa53e146c79ed0ee1530/b17f8/blogbg.jpg 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>\n<p>Illustration above is from my picture-book '\n<a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/book/the-